| code | `code-event-generate` | `code-event-generate` |
| code | `code-integrationtest-generate` | `code-integrationtest-generate` |
| code | `code-mapping-generate` | `code-mapping-generate` |
| code | `code-program-configure` | `code-program-configure` |
| code | `code-query-generate` | `code-query-generate` |
| code | `code-unittest-generate` | `code-unittest-generate` |
| code | `code-valueobject-generate` | `code-valueobject-generate` |
